    <item>
      <title>什么是黄金签证？在哪里可以获得？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/what-s-a-golden-visa-where-can-you-still-get-one-and-what-are-the-benefits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果一个国家的政府不欢迎你，那么试图进入另一个国家从未如此困难或危险。2023 年，移民在寻找新生活的过程中死亡人数创下历史新高，当时各国政府在边境执法方面投入了前所未有的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/what-s-a-golden-visa-where-can-you-still-get-one-and-what-are-the-benefits</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 08:41:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗预测改革将保护尼日利亚奈拉免受油价下跌的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/nigeria-s-naira-usd-ngn-how-reforms-could-buffer-naira-from-oil-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团首席非洲经济学家戴维·考恩表示，尼日利亚奈拉继续面临油价下跌的压力，不过结构性改革可能有助于其比过去更好地抵御经济衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/nigeria-s-naira-usd-ngn-how-reforms-could-buffer-naira-from-oil-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 08:30:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的 Fink 表示市场对美联储降息的预测是错误的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/blackrock-s-fink-says-market-is-wrong-to-bet-on-so-many-fed-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司首席执行官拉里芬克表示，鉴于美国经济持续增长，市场对美联储降息的预期过于强烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/blackrock-s-fink-says-market-is-wrong-to-bet-on-so-many-fed-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 08:13:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长雷恩表示，通胀放缓为 10 月降息提供依据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/ecb-s-rehn-says-direction-of-rates-is-clear-but-data-to-set-pace</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员奥利·雷恩称，通胀压力缓解和欧元区经济恶化为本月降息提供了理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/ecb-s-rehn-says-direction-of-rates-is-clear-but-data-to-set-pace</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德金融顾问称欧洲需要统一的银行市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/blackrock-s-fink-says-europe-needs-more-unified-banking-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司首席执行官拉里芬克敦促欧洲继续统一其银行市场，但未对德国商业银行和意大利联合信贷银行的潜在合并发表评论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/blackrock-s-fink-says-europe-needs-more-unified-banking-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 07:27:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管 2025 年利率决议存疑，美联储仍推动全球降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/central-bank-rate-cuts-fed-drives-global-push-despite-questions-over-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着全球通胀冲击的最后迹象逐渐消退，在各经济体迈向充满未知数的新年之际，降低借贷成本的举措即将保持势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/central-bank-rate-cuts-fed-drives-global-push-despite-questions-over-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>借款人打破全球纪录出售 6000 亿美元债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/borrowers-smash-global-records-to-sell-600-billion-in-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着收益率下降和美国总统大选临近，全球各地的公司和政府都在向债务市场注入大量债券和贷款，借入资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/borrowers-smash-global-records-to-sell-600-billion-in-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 22:08:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
